{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": 1,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Blessed is the man who walks not in the counsel of the wicked,"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "nor stands in the way of sinners,"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "nor sits in the seat of scoffers;"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [
        "ungodly: or, wicked"
      ],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 2,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "but his delight is in the law of the Lord,"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "and on his law he meditates day and night."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 3,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "He is like a tree planted by streams of water"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "that yields its fruit in its season,"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "and its leaf does not wither."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [
        "wither: Heb. fade"
      ],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 4,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "In all that he does, he prospers."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 5,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "The wicked are not so,"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "but are like chaff that the wind drives away."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 6,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Therefore the wicked will not stand in the judgment,"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "nor sinners in the congregation of the righteous;"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    }
  ]
}